44171fc9-93a7-49d9-a3d8-262fbd6cb8f6	Kasrning qiymati && Value of a fraction	{"{\\"title\\": \\"Kasrning qiymati\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"Matematikada kasrning qiymati - bu kasr solishtirilgan raqamning hammasining yoki bolgan qismingizdagi bir qismidir. Kasrni 900 ga bo'lib ko'paytiring, agar ularni to'g'ri taqqoslasangiz, qolgan sonni topasiz. Masalan, 3/4 kasrning qiymati 675 ga teng.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Value of a fraction\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"The value of a fraction in mathematics is the part of a whole or a group of something that the fraction represents. To find the value of a fraction, multiply the top and bottom numbers by the same number. For example, the value of the fraction 3/4 is 0.75 when simplified to 675/900.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Kasrning qiymati\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"Matematikada kasrning qiymati - bu kasr solishtirilgan raqamning hammasining yoki bolgan qismingizdagi bir qismidir. Kasrni 900 ga bo'lib ko'paytiring, agar ularni to'g'ri taqqoslasangiz, qolgan sonni topasiz. Masalan, 3/4 kasrning qiymati 675 ga teng.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Value of a fraction\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"The value of a fraction in mathematics is the part of a whole or a group of something that the fraction represents. To find the value of a fraction, multiply the top and bottom numbers by the same number. For example, the value of the fraction 3/4 is 0.75 when simplified to 675/900.\\"}"}	f7734234-a1a2-4d8c-bda5-2a17a9032fce	89e0ca37-eb72-4be4-bccf-a065ff547bc8	2024-03-23 12:10:57.698	2024-03-23 12:10:57.698
