e82bb134-dede-48f7-92a8-caecba492dca	. Arab tilida qisqiche ma'lumot va ma'qullar && . Brief information and proverbs in Arabic	{"{\\"title\\": \\"Arab tilida qisqiche ma'lumot\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"Arab tili - bu Semit tillar oilasiga mansub bo'lib, Yaqin Sharq va Shimoliy Afrika mamlakatlarida keng tarqalgan. Arab tilida yozuv chapdan o'ngga qarab yoziladi. U dunyodagi eng ko'p so'zlab yuritiladigan tillardan biri hisoblanadi va Qur'on kitobi ushbu tilda yozilgan.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Arab ma'qullari - 1\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"\\\\\\"من طلب العلا سهر الليالي\\\\\\" - \\\\\\"Kim oliy maqomlarni istasa, tunlarni bedor o'tkazar\\\\\\". Bu maqol yuqori maqsadlarga erishish uchun qattiq mehnat va fidoyilik zarurligini ifodalaydi.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Arab ma'qullari - 2\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"\\\\\\"الصبر مفتاح الفرج\\\\\\" - \\\\\\"Sabr murakkabliklarni yengishning kalitidir\\\\\\". Bu maqol insonlarga qiyin vaziyatlarda sabrli bo'lishning muhimligini eslatadi.\\"}","{\\"title\\": \\"Arab ma'qullari - 3\\", \\"uzContent\\": \\"\\\\\\"الكلام الطيب صدقة\\\\\\" - \\\\\\"Yaxshi so'z - sadqadir\\\\\\". Ushbu maqol tilning kuchini va yaxshi so'zlar bilan odamlarga yordam berishning muhimligini urg'ulaydi.\\"}"}	a07ca691-74e3-4914-8183-ce7f3f31d10d	120e7a6f-e883-4af0-b69f-8144fb01fa09	2024-03-24 14:50:28.072	2024-03-24 14:50:28.072
